COINS GOLD MONEY

   The coin system in Krynn is based upon war, as are all things.  Thus precious
metals such as gold, silver, platinum, while valuable, are not used as the
normal exchange since they have no real use in war.  Instead a system of weighted
coins of various metals used in weapon and armor smithing has been devised by
the populace.  The various metals and coin types are adamantine, mithril, steel
(which is the basic unit), bronze and copper.  

Below is the exchange ratio:

1 adamantite coin = 25 mithril coins
1 mithril coin = 100 steel coins
1 steel coin = 10 bronze coins
1 bronze coin = 10 copper coins

