allows a character to switch their active class to another class they possess, in
order to memorize spells.

The syntax is as follows:

setactive (no argument)
This will list the classes a character may choose from, preceeded by a number
Ie.
0) Mage
1) Cleric
4) Fighter

If you wanted to switch to fighter, you would then type "setactive 4"

See Also: MULTI-CLASSING MEMORIZATION SPELLS SCRIBE MAGIC

