CLASS-ABILITIES-INSPIRE-COMPETENCE
Inspire Competence (Su)

A bard of 3rd level or higher with 6 or more ranks in a Perform skill can use his music or 
poetics to help an ally succeed at a task. The ally must be within 30 feet and able to see 
and hear the bard. The bard must also be able to see the ally. 

The ally gets a +2 competence bonus on skill checks with a particular skill as long as he or
she continues to hear the bards music. Certain uses of this ability are infeasible. The 
effect lasts as long as the bard concentrates, up to a maximum of 2 minutes. A bard cant 
inspire competence in himself. Inspire competence is a mind-affecting ability. 

