CLASS-ABILITIES-FAST-MOVEMENT
Fast Movement (Ex)

A character with this class ability land speed is faster than the norm for his race by +10 feet. This benefit
applies only when he is wearing no armor, light armor, or medium armor and not carrying a heavy load. Apply
this bonus before modifying the land speed of a character with this ability because of any load carried
or armor worn.

