Uncanny Dodge (Ex)

At 2nd level, a character with this ability retains his Dexterity bonus to AC (if any) even if he  
is caught flat-footed or struck by an invisible attacker. However, he still loses his Dexterity bonus
to AC if immobilized. If a beserker already has uncanny dodge from a different class, he automatically 
gains improved uncanny dodge instead. 

