Timeless Body (Ex)

Druid:

After attaining 15th level, a druid no longer takes ability score penalties for aging and 
cannot be magically aged. Any penalties she may have already incurred, however, remain in 
place. Bonuses still accrue, and the druid still dies of old age when her time is up.. 


