Evasion (Ex)

Monk:

At 2nd level or higher if a monk makes a successful Reflex saving throw against an attack that 
normally deals half damage on a successful save, she instead takes no damage. Evasion can be 
used only if a monk is wearing light armor or no armor. A helpless monk does not gain the 
