ACCOUNT-EXPERIENCE

Account experience is used to unlock special features in the game such as
advanced races and prestige classes.  The main method of gaining account
experience is through role playing.  The second main method of gaining it
is by contributing content to the game, such as zones, socials, help files
and so forth.
 
