attacks you in melee. The flames also protect you from either cold-based or 
fire-based attacks (your choice).
@n
Any creature striking you with its body or a handheld weapon deals normal damage, 
but at the same time the attacker takes 1d6 points of damage +1 point per caster 
level (maximum +15). This damage is either cold damage (if the shield protects 
against fire-based attacks) or fire damage (if the shield protects against 
cold-based attacks). If the attacker has spell resistance, it applies to this 
effect. Creatures wielding weapons with exceptional reach are not subject to 
this damage if they attack you.
