thin and wispy, giving off light equal to only half the illumination of a 
normal torch (10 feet). The color of the flames is determined randomly 
(50% chance of either color)blue or green if the chill shield is cast, 
violet or blue if the warm shield is employed. The special powers of each 
version are as follows.
