RACE-AIR-GENESI
@nAir genasi see themselves as the inheritors of the sky, the wind, and the very
air of the world. They are most often neutral. They appear mostly human, with
one or two unusual traits reflecting their quasi-elemental nature, such as a
light blue color to their skin or hair, a slight breeze in their presence at all
times, or flesh that is cool to the touch. They care little for their appearance
and tend to have wind-tossed hair and much-mended clothes. Their emotions vary
quickly between calm reserve and great intensity.
@n
&YAir Genasi Characters&y:@n
@n +2 Dexterity, +2 Intelligence, -2 Wisdom, -2 Charisma
@n Medium Size, Base Speed 30 ft
@n Darkvision 60 feet
@n +2 Bluff, +2 Hide
@n
@n Special Attacks:     Levitate (as 5th level sorcerer)
@n Special Qualities:   +1 racial bonus vs air spells and effects
@n increases by +1 every five character levels
@n Clerical Focus:      Must choose a deity that grants the Air domain, and
@n must select Air as one of her two domains.
@n Breathless:          Air genasi do not need to breathe
@n Outsider:            Air genasi are native outsiders.
@n Automatic Languages: Common
@n Bonus Languages:     Any (Except secret languages, such as Druidic)
@n Favored Class:       Fighter
@n Level Adjustment:    +1
