RACE-DROW-ELF
@nDescended from the original dark-skinned elven subrace called the Illythiiri,
@nthe drow were cursed into their present appearance by the good elven deities for
@nfollowing the goddess Lolth down the path to evil and corruption. Also called
@ndark elves, the drow have black skin that resembles polished obsidian and stark
@nwhite or pale yellow hair. They commonly have very pale eyes in shades of pale
@nlilac, silver, pink, and blue. They also tend tobe smaller and thinner than most
@nelves. Most drowon the surface are evil and worship Vhaeraun, but some outcasts
@nand renegades have a more neutral attitude.
