RACE-DUERGAR
@nSometimes called gray dwarves, these evil begins dwell in the underground.
Most duergar are bald (even the females), and they dress in drab clothing that
is designed to blend into stone. In their lairs they may wear jewelry, but it
is always kept dull. They war with other dwarves, even allying with other
underground creatures from time to time.
@n
The duergar revere the deity Laduguer, a joyless god who demands constant toil.
