RACE-SVIRFNEBLIN
@nHidden in the depths of the Underdark live the svirfneblin, or deep gnomes.
Reclusive, suspicious, and resentful of intrusion into thri cavern homes, the
deep gnomes share little of the humor or openness of their surface cousins.
Where rock gnome community bursts with energy, excitement, and laughter, a
svirfneblin city is a dull and colorless place of echoing silence and furtive
motion in the shadows. All hands are raised against the svirfneblin - or so
the deep gnomes believe, anyway.
@n
@nSvirfneblin have gnarled physiques, brown or gray skin, gray eyes, and gray
hair (although males are bald). They tend to be sullen, withdrawn, and
suspicious to a fault.
@n
