GIFT-EXPERIENCE GIFT-ACCOUNT-EXPERIENCE

Gift experience can be given to other players to reward them for good role play,
helping you out, just because you like the other person, or used as currency to
purchase things.  It is normally gained as a percentage chance everytime you gain
regular experience.

The syntax is 'gift <character name> <reason>'

