CLASS-ABILITY-DRAGON-MOUNT-BREATH

Each rank with this class ability allows the rider to use their dragon mount's
breath weapon once per ten minutes.

The breath weapon will do energy damage equal to the dragon's current hit
points, or half damage on a successful reflex save.  DC is based on the rider's
dragon rider levels.

