RULES-EVIL

@RALL EVIL ROLE PLAY MUST BE KEPT RATED PG@n

When role playing your characters who are evil, you must keep all content rated
PG at all times.  We do not want to see graphic violence in your language or
descriptions, or extremely dark and twisted plots.  Voldemort of Harry potter or
Sauron of Lord of the Rings is the extent of our villainy here.  Those who attempt
to go further will be warned, and those who argue or do not desist immediately will
be punished.

Secondly, @Rthis is not a pk MUD!@n.  Attempts in using evil role play to incite
others to engage in pk with you will be dealt with harshly.  You may pk if you like,
but it should be part of a mutually consentual role played plot, and not the result
of you inciting someone to anger or mistreating them through role play or ooc conduct.
Those who act in such a manner will be warned, and those who argue or continue will be
punished.

I would like to say that we do not discourage evil role play at all, just the extent
of it.  We feel evil role play is a valuable, even essential part of having a fun
game.  After all if there are no bad guys who are the good guys going to fight.

Also we are currently making plans to implement a robust pk system in which consentual
pvp play can take place, including special awards for those who take part unavailable
any other way.

