RULES-VALUES

@RDO UNTO OTHERS AS YOU WOULD HAVE OTHERS DO UNTO YOU@n

This game is created and managed on good values and high standards.  If you are
to play here, we expect you to act in accordance with the values of honesty, kindness,
patience, tolerance and courtesy in all out of character behavior.  We exhort all to
live by the standard of the golden rule, 'Do unto others as you would have others
do unto you', but at the very least you must abide by that rule while on this game.
We do not expect perfection, but we do expect players to do their best, and to do
their best to correct and make up for any mistakes they make in their conduct with
other players or staff.

