CLASS-FEATS

  Class feats are feats obtained that can be selected from a certain list
and only while a certain class is active.  Each class has it's own counter
of class feats, so if you gain a level in fighter for example, you will have
to spend your class feat before you take a different class, or you will have
to wait until you take a level in fighter again before you can spend it.

To see the available class feats for your current class, type '@Cfeats available
classfeats@n'.

