skills. In order to raise these skills, practice sessions must be spent at a
trainer (such as Jolin in Luskan). Class skills cost 1 practice, while cross-
class and language skills cost 2 practice sessions (unless you have the Able
Learner feat, in which case all skills cost 1 session).
