BOUNTY BOUNTIES

The bounty system is the primary way for adventurers to earn gold in the game.
The system works by assigning you a number of mobs to kill, based on the mobs
that are currently loaded in the world and around your level.  The more mobs
you are asked to kill the greater the rewards will be.  Rewards include gold,
quest points, experience and a chance for a random magic item as well.

To take a new bounty type @Ybounty new@n.
Optionally, you can specify a particular mob to get a bounty on by typing
