BACKUP REIMBURSEMENTS

  The backup command allows you to create a copy of your equipment file at
any time.  If, for any reason you lose your equipment, you can talk to a staff
member, and they can instantly reimburse all of your equipment with a single
command.  The equipment that will be reimbursed will be the same as the last
time you used the backup command, so please use it often.

We warn against using the backup command with triggers or aliases, because if
you lose your equipment somehow, and backup, your reimbursement will not include
any equipment, because the backup will be a copy of your equipment when you had
none.

Regarding reimbursements, we will generally reimburse you equipment for any
instance of a game bug, or through being scammed in some way by another player.
Losing equipment in any other way does not qualify for a reimbursement.  We also
generally do not reimburse gold on hand, though we will reimburse bank gold
if somehow that is lost through a game bug.

In all cases with reimbursements we will give the player the benefit of the
doubt.  However if we do find someone has cheated or lied to us, justice will
be swift and harsh, so please do not abuse our kindness.

Also note that it is your responsibility to keep your equipment backed up.
We will not do manual reimbursements, so either back up, or risk losing
everything.

