WISHLISTS WISH-LISTS

Wish Lists:
 
Your wish list is a list of items that you prefer to find when you receive
random treasure.  Currently the system only supports weapons, armor and
shields, however more will be added in the future as the random treasure
system is improved upon.
 
The command to us is 'wishlist' and it has 3 options: list, show and erase.
The fourth option is to enter the name of the item you wish to add to the list.
 
'List' will display the correct spellings of all items you are able to add
to the wish list.

'Show' will display your current wish list.

'Erase' will delete everything on your wish list, allowing you to start anew.

Items on your wish list will appear in random treasure about twice as often
as other random items.  However, you will only get a weapon on your wish list
if the treasure table rolls for a weapon, and then rolls for your wish list
item.  Having a wish list does not increase the chance of finding magical
items, or specific types of magical items, only increasing the chance of
finding something useful when the appropriate type of item is rolled.

