AUGMENT

AUGMENTING CRYSTALS

By putting more than one crystal of the same type in a crafting station, one is
able to augment the power of the most powerful crystal, destroying all other crystals
in the process.

First find a crafting station.  Then select the crystals of the same type (for example
AC_DEFLECTION) and put as many as you want, at least two, in the crafting station.
Type augment and you will be able to increase the level of the most powerful crystal therein.

For example, if you had a level 20 crystal, a level 10 crystal, and a level 16 crystal, you
would be augmenting the level 20 crystal.  The amount it is augmented is the level of each
crystal within divided by 4 (not total levels, individual crystal levels).  So in the example
above, we would end up with a 20 + 2 (10 / 4) + 4 (16 / 4) or level 26 crystal.

Augmenting does not require any special training to perform.

See Also: @YCRAFTING@n
