The Neidar (knoll dwellers) are the name given to those dwarves who at the time 
of the creation of Thorbardin chose to live outside. All hill dwarves are grouped 
into this thanedom. Many of these dwarves could trace their ancestry back to one 
of the other clans. The role of the Neidar prior to the Cataclysm was scouting and 
tending to the flocks outside of Thorbardin. Led by Cale Greeneye, this group was 
indispensable during the war against the wizards and the fight against Rage.
