RACE-DAERGAR-DWARF
The Daergar are also one of the original clans of Kal-Thax. One of their earliest 
known thanes was Vog Ironface, who ruled at the time of the Hylar's arrival. 
After the Hylar's arrival the Daergar played several important roles in the 
Wizards War and the wars against the Empire of Ergoth.

Daergar are the counterparts of the Theiwar in much the same way the Daewar 
