COPYOVER HOT-REBOOT

A copyover or hot reboot occurs normally when new code is entering the game.

The process will restart the game without disconnecting anyone.  It generally
takes 5-60 seconds to complete.

A copyover will be set to a pending state if anyone in the game is doing any of
the following:
Crafting (any type of action)
Fighting
Levelling Up
Setting Descriptions in Character Generation

If any of those actions are taking place on the mud, the copyover will be cancelled
but no further actions of those types will be able to take place.  The imm may try
again every minute or two to check if the actions have been completed, and when they
are, the copyover will go through successfully.

