RACE-SOLAMNIC
Solamnics, also referred to as Solamnian or Solamnan, are mostly 
a human people from the nation of Solamnia that are the descendants 
of Ergothian and Kharolian blood. The people began calling themselves 
Solamnics after farmers and peasants named their new nation Solamnia 
