CLASS-KNIGHT-OF-THE-CROWN

Knight of the Crown Prestige Class

REQUIREMENTS:
Alignment: Lawful Good Only
Must be sponsored by immortal or other knight of the crown (@Yhelp sponsor@n)
Minimum Base Attack Bonus +3
Minimum Fortitude Save +4
Minimum Diplomacy Skill +2
Minimum Ride Skill +2
Must Have the Following Feats: Heavy Armor Proficiency, Honorbound, Martial Weapon
  Proficiency, Shield Proficiency

BENEFITS:
Gains +1 to Base Attack Bonus Per Level
Saving Throws: Fortitude (High), Reflex & Willpower (Low)
Class Skills: Diplomacy, Intimidate, Ride
Skill Points / Level: 2 + Intelligence Modifier
Extra Combat Class Feat Every Level Divisible by 3

CLASS ABILITIES: 
(1) Simple Weapon Proficiency, Martial Weapon Proficiency, Strength of Honor,\
(1) Knightly Courage
(2) Heroic Initiative
(3) Diehard
(4) Honorable Will, Strength of Honor
(5) Heroic Initiative
(6) Might of Honor, Armored Mobility
(7) Strength of Honor
(8) Heroic Initiative
(9) Aura of Courage
(10) Crown of Knighthood, Strength of Honor

DESCRIPTION:
Knights of the Crown are those among the Knights of Solamnia's lowest order
of knighthood, and thus are the most plentiful and often act as foot soldiers
or guardsmen.  They follow the principles of obedience and loyalty above all else
and their patron deity is Habbakuk.  They live by the code "My Honor is My Life" and
are also required to know and live by the Measure of the Knights of Solamnia.

They are chivalrous, generally distrust magic, and stand for all that is good and
upright.  They are the defenders of Solamnia, and the free nations of Ansalon.

See Also: CLASS KNIGHT OF THE SWORD, CLASS KNIGHT OF THE ROSE, CLASS PALADIN
