SUPPLY-ORDERS SUPPLY
The supply order system is a good way to get started building up Artisan experience.
Similar to the bounty system, you are assigned a number of items to craft and will
receive gold and Artisan experience upon completion of the order.
You also receive Artisan experience while crafting each item in the order.

To get started, find Blasia in the Palanthas Crafting Halls and type @Ysupplyorder new@n
Once you have accepted an order, find a crafting station and type @Ysupplyorder@n to
see what materials are required.  @YPut@n the required materials in the crafting station
and type @Ysupplyorder@n again to begin crafting the item.

Once you have completed the required number of items to fulfill the order, return to Blasia
and type @Ysupplyorder complete@n to receive your reward.

See also: @YCRAFTING@n, @YHARVESTING@n
