BINDING-ITEMS BOUND-ITEMS REBIND
All equipment must be bound to your character before it can be equipped.  This
process uses your knowledge skill to determine whether it can be done successfully.
If you do not have a good knowledge skill, then you are better off going to a binding
shop and having it done for you.  One of these can be found just west of Palanthas
